{"tid":1567891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日淘大 做法不完美 可接受 可改善！","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:06:58.000Z","uid":89974,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"32fa5e6d213bd38307fe54d123b723ff9cb58ad1","tid":1567891,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:39:10.000Z","msg":"藍屍一定要打，再俾佢毫無代價咁打手足，下次就唔止係傷而係死<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寶琳個位記者俾人斬到瀕死唔記得咗拿！？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地今日企得出嚟，已經勇過80%香港人！<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗咩放頭唔送頭，你地真心覺得要做既野唔駛理其他人意見！有班人永遠只會腦內補完最唔送頭既方案，到前線真係心灰意冷/俾人拉哂個陣，你會發現無一個冷氣軍師會出嚟組團，永遠只會食花生！食到入集中營！<br />\n<br />\n無論做乜都好，只要唔做左膠，我地核爆都唔割！俾人拉上庭我地坐旁聽！你要掩護我地做街坊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯一要改善既點係打完要即走！甚至唔好等集合，空襲佢地，一擊脫離！咁樣係最安全亦都最令人驚既做法！<br />\n否則當狗圍埋嚟處境就非常危險！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸於勇武！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d35a4d306872fd66adaa518106571f5806ddb2b","tid":1567891,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d18917e0579bb46b790b6bed81c9dba604f0f7e","tid":1567891,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc0e9d81f2072798a821033ec206dfe2d56e6c85","tid":1567891,"uid":156145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸於勇武"},{"pid":"64704890805f5908824a9c2341d066d561780898","tid":1567891,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0caa68ec04cbe430fbee64ed271183af3a28f10","tid":1567891,"uid":147367,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見狗即走</span></span>"},{"pid":"22d92c04cbdc1e9e97